title: Easy corned beef hash
ingredients: ['1 (340g) tin corned beef, chilled, cut into bite-sized cubes', '1 (415g) tin baked beans', '1 (300g) tin sliced carrots, drained', '1 (300g) tin garden peas, drained', '1 (300g) tin new potatoes, drained and quartered', 'tomato ketchup to taste', 'grated cheese to taste']
